Parallax engine (vendored)
Copyright 2026 Mario Mercaldi

This directory is a vendored copy of the package-neutral Parallax detection
engine (formerly published as `prlx-engine`, importable here as `engine`),
taken verbatim from the `parallax/prlx/prlx/` package. It is the deterministic
code-understanding substrate: source -> taxonomy atoms, dataflow, callgraph,
scan-report assembly. Logic is unchanged from upstream.

Bundled taxonomy signatures under `taxonomy/signatures/` are a verbatim copy of
`parallax-taxonomy/signatures/` (the callee-to-atom signature pack + its schema),
which the engine reads at runtime to classify extracted callees into ontology
atoms.

